Phil Knight - Wikipedia






















 






Phil Knight

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"Philip Knight" redirects here. For the English cricketer, see Philip Knight (cricketer).
"Phillip Knight" redirects here. For the footballer, see Phillip Knight (footballer).


Phil Knight



Knight in 2010



Born
Philip Hampson Knight
(1938-02-24) February 24, 1938 (age 79)
Portland, Oregon, U.S.


Citizenship
United States


Alma mater
University of Oregon
Stanford University


Occupation
Chairman emeritus of Nike, Inc.


Net worth
 US$24.4 billion (October 2016) [1]


