 Phil Knight
(I)





Phil Knight was born on February 24, 1938 in Portland, Oregon, USA as Philip Hampson Knight. He has been married to Penelope Parks since September 13, 1968. They have three children.            
See full bio »
            
 


Born:

February 24, 
     
